<!-- Definition and medical uses -->
'''吡嗪醯胺'''（ {{lang-en|Pyrazinamide}}），是一種治療[[結核病|結核病]]的藥物<ref name=AHFS2016>{{cite web|title=Pyrazinamide|url=https://www.drugs.com/monograph/pyrazinamide.html|publisher=The American Society of Health-System Pharmacists|access-date=8 December 2016|url-status=no|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161220231056/https://www.drugs.com/monograph/pyrazinamide.html|archive-date=2016-12-20}}</ref>。在治療開放性結核病時，通常會與[[利福平|利福平]]、[[異煙肼|異煙肼]]、[[鏈黴素|鏈黴素]]或[[乙胺丁醇|乙胺丁醇]]一起使用<ref name=WHO2008>{{cite book | title = WHO Model Formulary | year = 2009 | isbn = 978-9241547659 | vauthors = ((World Health Organization)) | veditors = Stuart MC, Kouimtzi M, Hill SR | hdl = 10665/44053 | author-link = World Health Organization | publisher = World Health Organization | hdl-access=free |pages=136, 140, 594, 608 }}</ref>。一般不建議用於治療潛伏性結核病<ref name=AHFS2016/>。給藥途徑為口服<ref name=Ric2015>{{cite book|last1=Hamilton|first1=Richart | name-list-style = vanc |title=Tarascon Pocket Pharmacopoeia 2015 Deluxe Lab-Coat Edition|date=2015|publisher=Jones & Bartlett Learning|isbn=9781284057560|page=415}}</ref>。

<!-- Side effects and mechanism -->
常見的副作用為噁心、食慾降低、肌肉與關節疼痛及引起[[疹|皮疹]]<ref name=AHFS2016/><ref name=":2">{{Cite book|title=Medical-surgical nursing : assessment and management of clinical problems|last1=Lewis|first1=Sharon Mantik|last2=Dirksen|first2=Shannon Ruff|last3=Heitkemper|first3=Margaret M.|last4=Bucher|first4=Linda|last5=Harding|first5=Mariann|date=5 December 2013|isbn=978-0-323-10089-2|edition=9th|location=St. Louis, MO|oclc=228373703}}</ref>。嚴重一點的副作用可能會發作[[痛風|痛風]]、{{le|肝中毒|liver toxicity}}}及對陽光較為敏感<ref name=AHFS2016/>。不建議用於患有嚴重肝病或[[紫質症|紫質症]]的患者身上。[[妊娠|懷孕]]期間用藥是否安全目前尚不明朗，[[母乳哺育|哺乳]]期間用藥則相對安全。本品為{{le|抗分枝桿菌|antimycobacterial}}類藥物<ref name=AHFS2016/>，目前相關藥理機轉尚待闡明<ref name=AHFS2016/>。

<!-- History and culture -->
吡嗪醯胺問世於 1936 年，到 1972 年才廣泛使用<ref>{{cite book|last1=Donald|first1=P. R.|last2=van Helden|first2=P. D.|title=Antituberculosis Chemotherapy|date=2011|publisher=Karger Medical and Scientific Publishers|isbn=978-3805596282|page=8|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=aZc7AQAAQBAJ&pg=PA8|language=en|url-status=no|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210429110301/https://books.google.com/books?id=aZc7AQAAQBAJ&pg=PA8|archive-date=2021-04-29|access-date=2021-06-14}}</ref>。本品名列[[世界衛生組織基本藥物標準清單|世界衛生組織基本藥物標準清單]]中，認可為[[醫療系統|醫療系統]]中最安全有效的必需藥物<ref name="WHO21st">{{cite book | vauthors = ((World Health Organization)) | title = World Health Organization model list of essential medicines: 21st list | year = 2019 | hdl = 10665/325771 | author-link = World Health Organization | publisher = World Health Organization | location = Geneva | id = WHO/MVP/EMP/IAU/2019.06. License: CC BY-NC-SA 3.0 IGO | hdl-access=free }}</ref>。

